Jack Harper admits Gareth Bale is his inspiration at Real Madrid but the Scottish youngster was never starstruck and even offered to help the Welshman settle in at the Bernabeu.

Real academy prospect Harper was just 17 when Bale joined the club for £86million last summer.

Born in Spain to Scottish parents, striker Harper has been with Real since he was 13 and is used to rubbing shoulders with the likes of Bale, Cristiano Ronaldo and the rest of Carlo Ancelotti's star-studded European champions.

